import React from 'react';
import {Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input} from 'reactstrap'


const sumbitFormA = (event) => {
    alert(`Name: ${FormA.name.value} Value: ${this.value.value} Weight: ${this.weight.value}`)
    event.preventDefaul()
}



const FormA = () => {


    return (

    <Form onSubmit={sumbitFormA}>
        <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="name">Name</Label>
            <Input type="text" id='name' name='name' innerRef={ input => this.name = input}/>
        </FormGroup>

        <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="value">Value</Label>
            <Input type="text" id='value' name='value' innerRef={input => this.value = input}/>
        </FormGroup>

        <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="weight">Weight</Label>
            <Input type="text" id='weight' name='weight' innerRef={input => this.value = input}/>
        </FormGroup>

            <Button type='submit' value='submit' color='primary'>Login</Button>
    </Form>

    )
}

export default FormA
